data.description: LOVELY CARSON HOME!!! Great Mid Century Modern Design!!! Major Price Reduction!!! MOTIVATED SELLER!!! This single story property features 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, bright & open floorplan highlighted with a  cheery atrium in the middle of the home giving easy access to  privately relaxing & enjoying the outdoors. Vaulted ceilings, recessed lighting, fireplace in the living room, great dining room, nice kitchen, recent interior paint  throughout, newer flooring installed, updated master bedroom & bath, central A/C & heating, 2 car attached garage for direct  home entry,  new energy efficient roof, lifetime exterior paint,  entire home has new cooper plumbing , great family neighborhood, excellent corner lot with large back & side yards for entertaining, great curb appeal beautifully landscaped, newly installed turf. Centrally located near freeways, schools, Cal State Dominguez Hills College, restaurants, South Bay Pavilion shopping mall, Dignity Health Sports Center & more. WELCOME HOME!!!!
